      },
      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> the crater lake's apex horrors — <em>several</em> of these Gargantuan swimming worms haunt the 800-ft black depths. Any creature entering the water (or boating it) without stealth quickly draws one; another lurks off the ruined quay at the hidden mooring (B37), surging at anything within 20 feet of the shore. <strong>Morale:</strong> the B37 worm retreats to the depths below ~60 HP. They cannot leave the lake — and their meat is too foul even for Belshallam.</p>",
